<br>
Typically you can easily tell a bard by her songs, so I never worried the similiarity in names. The people who know me know who I am - and if someone blames me for the actions of a relative it is their worry not mine ne?<br>
<br>
I remember however on another beta world, the Realm, where the server wiped characters and we would all race to reserve our names and those of our friends from the exploiters and namestealers. At least Verant does not put us through this LOL.<br>
